  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Education for Holocaust Remembrance (Special Account)</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project promotes the inclusion of Holocaust history in national educational systems as a means of combating racism and raising awareness on the mechanisms of State violence so as to contribute to the prevention of genocide and mass atrocities. It seeks to achieve greater integration of Holocaust education world-wide by supporting the efforts of interested governments and of the civil society and reinforcing links between NGOs, memorial museums, therefore furthering the exchange of expertise and of good practices as well as the diffusion of relevant materials at an international level.</narrative>
  </description>
